Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.03,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,青リンゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.95,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱えてる胸の奥
